casebody.data:
William L. ROUSAN, petitioner,
v.
George A. LOMBARDI, Director, Missouri Department of Corrections, et al. No. 13-9835 (13A1063). Supreme Court of the United States April 22, 2014.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice ALITO

*1933and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied.
